<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-bs-theme="dark">
<head prefix="og: https://ogp.me/ns#">
    <%- include('snippets/head.ejs'); %>
    <title>Home - WaifuVault</title>
    <link href="assets/custom/css/index.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

<main>
    <!-- Modal for Albums -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="albumsModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="albumsModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="albumsModalLabel">Albums Feature</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>
                        <strong>Albums</strong> are a powerful way to organise and share collections of files hosted in
                        your buckets.
                        This feature allows you to group multiple files into a single album and share it using a public
                        URL.
                        Anyone with the link gets a
                        <strong>read-only view</strong>, ensuring that your content remains secure and unalterable.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Whether you're showcasing media collections, collaborating on a project, or simply sharing files
                        with friends,
                        Albums make it easy to:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Organise Files:</strong> Group files logically within your buckets for easy access
                            and management.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Share Seamlessly:</strong> Generate a single public URL for the entire album and
                            share it with anyone.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Privacy Focus:</strong> Maintain control with read-only access for viewers,
                            preventing unauthorised edits.
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Custom Views:</strong> Display albums beautifully for a great sharing experience.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Multiple albums per bucket:</strong> Each bucket can contain multiple albums, share
                            and revoke the share at will.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        Create a bucket now and start using Albums to and enjoy effortless file sharing with enhanced
                        organisation and privacy!
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                    <a href="/bucketAccess" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Create a bucket</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Modals -->
    <!-- Encrypted Files Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="encryptedFilesModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="encryptedFilesModalLabel"
         aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="encryptedFilesModalLabel">Encrypted Files</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Your files can be secured using industry-leading AES-256 encryption, for your security and
                        privacy. The password is not stored, and the file can only be decrypted by people you provide
                        the password to. Even we cannot decrypt the file should you lose the password.</p>
                    <p>When you upload a file, you can set a password on it. Only users you provide with the password
                        can access the file.</p>
                    <p>Perfect for sensitive data, privacy concerns and secure file sharing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hide Filenames Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="hideFilenamesModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="hideFilenamesModalLabel"
         aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="hideFilenamesModalLabel">Hide Filenames</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>The original filename of a file that is uploaded can be hidden at your choice.</p>
                    <p>This allows you to use shortened, anonymous URLs to share files, without revealing potentially
                        sensitive details from the filename.</p>
                    <p>A simple checkbox can be set on upload to do this.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Custom Retention Period Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="customRetentionModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="customRetentionModalLabel"
         aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="customRetentionModalLabel">Custom Retention Period</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>You can choose how long your files are stored for. From as little as one minute, all the way up
                        to one year. You are in control of your data's lifespan.</p>
                    <p>You also have the ability to set a file to be removed once it has been downloaded - as a one-time
                        download.</p>
                    <p>This feature allows you to confidently share files, knowing they will only exist long enough to
                        be transferred if you want or long enough to be useful if that's what you need.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Buckets Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="bucketsModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="bucketsModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="bucketsModalLabel">Buckets</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Upload can be organized using our anonymous buckets feature. These are collections of files that
                        you have access to with a random unique key. No identifying information is used.</p>
                    <p>With the key, you can access an administration interface that allows you to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Track Statistics - types of uploads, sizes of uploads and upload velocity</li>
                        <li>Manage Files - upload files, remove files and change options for files</li>
                        <li>Manage Albums - create albums, share albums and remove albums</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Keep everything neatly sorted and managed without needing an account.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                    <a href="/bucketAccess" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Create a bucket</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Secure Sharing Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="secureSharingModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="secureSharingModalLabel"
         aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="secureSharingModalLabel">Secure Sharing</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>Your files can be confidently shared knowing that they have end-to-end encryption, ensuring that
                        only the intended recipients can view your files.</p>
                    <p>File URLs are unique and not easily guessable, making sure only those you provide the URL to will
                        be able to download them.</p>
                    <p>This is combined with our other file features of password protection and the ability to set one
                        time downloads, to provide a state of the art temporary file sharing system.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container py-4">
        <header class="pb-3 mb-4 border-bottom d-flex justify-content-between">
            <a href="/" class="text-body-emphasis text-decoration-none">
